data.description: Beautiful Lowcountry home featuring double wrapped porches, vaulted ceilings and updated kitchen. Open living space w/ gas fireplace, built-ins, hardwoods, four sets of French doors, and tons of natural light. Second floor owner's suite leads to another oversized deck with marsh and water views of Battery Creek. Fully fenced in yard with spacious 2 car garage and storage. Community amenities include deep water dock and boat launch, swimming pool, clubhouse, playground and more. Battery Point is close to all shopping and downtown Beaufort.
